HEADWORD: Flectional
<hw>Flec"tion*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of, or
pertaining to, flection or inflection.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>flectional</qex> word is a phrase in the bud.</q>
<rj><qau>Earle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Flector</ent>⟦br⟧
